 ############################
 VIM COMPILATION
 ############################  

 base compile
 ============

 to compile vim
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 | ./configure --prefix=/usr/local --with-x --with-features=huge	|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------ 
 It is useful to compile vim, using the next option
 (for using the clipboard in X envirement)
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
 | clipboard								|
 ------------------------------------------------------------------------
